Package: canopymap
Title: Map Nodes and Their Connections
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Nico", "Hawley-Weld", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Claude", "Sonnet 4.6", role = "ctb"))
Description: Creates interactive Leaflet maps of organizations with optional
    routing connections between nearest neighbors. Supports data from Google
    Sheets or local data frames, with configurable column names for use with
    any dataset.
